---
import HiddenGrammarLayout from '../../layouts/HiddenGrammarLayout.astro';
import poles from '../../data/hg-poles.json';
---

<HiddenGrammarLayout
  title="Framework"
  description="The structural system behind Art Lab's analysis — 11 Roots, 54 Principles, and the 4 Poles that organize every visual decision."
>
  <div class="hg-page fw-page">

    <header class="fw-header">
      <p class="fw-label">Framework</p>
      <h1 class="fw-title">Art Lab Framework</h1>
      <p class="fw-subtitle">The structural system behind the analysis — what the 11 Roots, 54 Principles, and 4 Poles are, how they connect, and why the framework is built this way.</p>
    </header>

    <!-- Foundation -->
    <section class="fw-section">
      <h2 class="fw-h2">The foundation</h2>
      <p>Art Lab is built on a single bet: that visual response is not magic, but mechanism. A discoverable code. The goal is to map that code — not to produce meaning, but to create the conditions under which meaning can be claimed responsibly.</p>
      <p>The move from mechanism to interpretation always requires judgment that no procedure can supply. The framework traces the mechanism. You supply the judgment.</p>

      <div class="fw-method">
        <p class="fw-method-label">Three simultaneous layers</p>
        <div class="fw-method-rows">
          <div class="fw-method-row">
            <span class="fw-method-num">1</span>
            <div>
              <strong>The Root (Shoresh)</strong>
              <p>The conceptual category — the structural DNA of what's happening in the work.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="fw-method-row">
            <span class="fw-method-num">2</span>
            <div>
              <strong>The Neural Fact</strong>
              <p>The biological mechanism — what your visual system is actually doing in response.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="fw-method-row">
            <span class="fw-method-num">3</span>
            <div>
              <strong>The Interpretive Hypothesis</strong>
              <p>Meaning — claimed only after the Evidence Gate passes, held as competing readings, not conclusions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Signal teaser -->
    <div class="fw-signal-teaser">
      <p>Some of the 54 Principles map onto things your visual system processes before you've formed a conscious thought — contrast, edge detection, figure-ground. Others are structural: rhythm, tension, spatial relationships that create conditions for a response rather than triggering one directly. The framework tracks both, because both shape what a viewer feels before they decide what to think.</p>
      <a href="/hidden-grammar/principles" class="fw-signal-link">Browse the 54 Principles →</a>
    </div>

    <!-- The 4 Poles -->
    <section class="fw-section">
      <h2 class="fw-h2">The 4 Poles</h2>
      <p class="fw-section-lead">Conceptual axes that modulate interpretation after Roots are established. Poles constrain conclusions — they do not generate them.</p>

      <div class="fw-system-rules">
        <p class="fw-rules-label">System Rules</p>
        <ul class="fw-rules-list">
          {poles.systemRules.map((rule) => (
            <li>{rule}</li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="fw-poles-grid">
        {poles.poles.map((pole) => (
          <article class="fw-pole-card">
            <div class="fw-pole-header">
              <h3 class="fw-pole-name">{pole.name}</h3>
              <span class="fw-pole-hebrew">{pole.hebrew}</span>
            </div>

            <div class="fw-pole-axis">
              <span class="fw-axis-label">Opposite axis:</span>
              <strong>{pole.axis.oppositeName}</strong>
            </div>

            <div class="fw-pole-body">
              <div class="fw-pole-block">
                <h4 class="fw-pole-h4">Governs</h4>
                <p>{pole.governs}</p>
              </div>

              <div class="fw-pole-block">
                <h4 class="fw-pole-h4">Function</h4>
                <p>{pole.function}</p>
              </div>

              <div class="fw-pole-block fw-pole-block--warning">
                <h4 class="fw-pole-h4">What this is NOT</h4>
                <ul class="fw-not-list">
                  {pole.notThis.map((item) => (
                    <li>{item}</li>
                  ))}
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="fw-pole-block">
                <h4 class="fw-pole-h4">Activation Conditions</h4>
                <ul class="fw-plain-list">
                  {pole.activationConditions.map((cond) => (
                    <li>{cond}</li>
                  ))}
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="fw-pole-block fw-pole-block--muted">
                <h4 class="fw-pole-h4">Failure Mode</h4>
                <p class="fw-italic">{pole.failureMode}</p>
              </div>

              <div class="fw-pole-block fw-pole-block--muted">
                <h4 class="fw-pole-h4">Override Limits</h4>
                <div class="fw-limits-grid">
                  <div>
                    <p class="fw-limits-label fw-limits-label--may">May:</p>
                    <ul class="fw-plain-list">
                      {pole.overrideLimits.may.map((item) => (
                        <li>{item}</li>
                      ))}
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="fw-limits-label fw-limits-label--maynot">May Not:</p>
                    <ul class="fw-plain-list">
                      {pole.overrideLimits.mayNot.map((item) => (
                        <li>{item}</li>
                      ))}
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="fw-axes-diagram">
        <p class="fw-axes-label">The Two Axes</p>
        <div class="fw-axes">
          <div class="fw-axis">
            <div class="fw-axis-line">
              <span class="fw-pole-end">Abstraction</span>
              <span class="fw-axis-arrow">↔</span>
              <span class="fw-pole-end">Realism</span>
            </div>
            <p class="fw-axis-desc">Distance from vs. closeness to depiction</p>
          </div>
          <div class="fw-axis">
            <div class="fw-axis-line">
              <span class="fw-pole-end">Witness</span>
              <span class="fw-axis-arrow">↔</span>
              <span class="fw-pole-end">Repair</span>
            </div>
            <p class="fw-axis-desc">Sustaining tension vs. moving toward resolution</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- RAP Protocol -->
    <section class="fw-section">
      <h2 class="fw-h2">Root Access Protocol (RAP)</h2>
      <p class="fw-section-lead">The Evidence Gate that prevents premature meaning collapse. Roots are locked until sufficient perceptual evidence has been gathered.</p>

      <div class="fw-rap-flow">
        <div class="fw-rap-phase">
          <span class="fw-phase-num">0</span>
          <h3>Declare Primary Action</h3>
          <p>Stripping / Building / Holding / Integrating</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fw-rap-arrow">↓</div>
        <div class="fw-rap-phase">
          <span class="fw-phase-num">1</span>
          <h3>Hold Zone</h3>
          <p>Visual Inventory + Snag Map — no Roots, no Meaning</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fw-rap-arrow">↓</div>
        <div class="fw-rap-phase">
          <span class="fw-phase-num">2</span>
          <h3>Mechanism Mapping</h3>
          <p>Pick 3–5 Principles (Principle-First)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fw-rap-arrow">↓</div>
        <div class="fw-rap-gate">
          <h3>Evidence Gate</h3>
          <p>Requirements to pass:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Coverage: 3+ Principles mapped</li>
            <li>Resistance: 1+ snag explained</li>
            <li>Constraint: 1+ absence named</li>
            <li>Uncertainty: 1+ ambiguity alive</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="fw-rap-arrow">↓</div>
        <div class="fw-rap-phase fw-rap-phase--unlocked">
          <span class="fw-phase-num fw-phase-num--green">4</span>
          <h3>Root Access</h3>
          <p>Max 2 Roots, with paid evidence</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fw-rap-arrow">↓</div>
        <div class="fw-rap-phase">
          <span class="fw-phase-num">5</span>
          <h3>Meaning as Hypotheses</h3>
          <p>2 competing interpretations — not verdicts</p>
          <p class="fw-phase-note">Unresolved tension between competing readings is a quality signal. It means the work is holding complexity rather than delivering a premature verdict.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fw-rap-arrow">↓</div>
        <div class="fw-rap-phase">
          <span class="fw-phase-num">6</span>
          <h3>Controlled Collapse</h3>
          <p>Choose best reading if evidence supports it</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="fw-pricing-rule">
        <p class="fw-rules-label">Pricing Rule</p>
        <p>You get <strong>3 meaning claims total</strong> in an analysis. Each meaning claim must pay with <strong>2 citations</strong> from evidence. No payment — no claim.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Nav -->
    <div class="fw-nav">
      <a href="/hidden-grammar" class="hg-btn hg-btn--ghost">← Art Lab</a>
      <a href="/hidden-grammar/toolkit" class="hg-btn hg-btn--primary">Open the Toolkit →</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</HiddenGrammarLayout>

<style>
  .fw-page {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  /* ── Header ─────────────────────────────────── */
  .fw-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
  }

  .fw-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #4f46e5;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .fw-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin: 0 0 0.875rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .fw-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  /* ── Sections ────────────────────────────────── */
  .fw-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  }

  .fw-section:last-of-type {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .fw-h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1e293b;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .fw-page p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: #334155;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .fw-section-lead {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── Method box ──────────────────────────────── */
  .fw-method {
    background: #f8fafc;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .fw-method-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #4f46e5;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .fw-method-rows {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .fw-method-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .fw-method-num {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    background: #4f46e5;
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 0.125rem;
  }

  .fw-method-row strong {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1e293b;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .fw-method-row p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: #475569;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Signal teaser ───────────────────────────── */
  .fw-signal-teaser {
    background: #f8fafc;
    border-left: 3px solid #4f46e5;
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    margin: 0 0 3rem;
  }

  .fw-signal-teaser p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #334155;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .fw-signal-link {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #4f46e5;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .fw-signal-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* ── System rules ────────────────────────────── */
  .fw-system-rules {
    background: #f8fafc;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .fw-rules-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #64748b;
    margin: 0 0 0.875rem;
  }

  .fw-rules-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .fw-rules-list li {
    padding: 0.625rem 0.875rem;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-left: 3px solid #4f46e5;
    border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: #334155;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ── Poles grid ──────────────────────────────── */
  .fw-poles-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(min(100%, 360px), 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .fw-pole-card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .fw-pole-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.875rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
  }

  .fw-pole-name {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1e293b;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .fw-pole-hebrew {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #4f46e5;
    font-weight: 600;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .fw-pole-axis {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: #f8fafc;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #334155;
  }

  .fw-axis-label {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .fw-pole-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.875rem;
  }

  .fw-pole-h4 {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #64748b;
    margin: 0 0 0.375rem;
  }

  .fw-pole-block p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: #334155;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .fw-pole-block--warning {
    background: #fef2f2;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 0.75rem;
  }

  .fw-pole-block--muted {
    background: #f8fafc;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 0.75rem;
  }

  .fw-not-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.375rem;
  }

  .fw-not-list li {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    background: #dc2626;
    color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.625rem;
  }

  .fw-plain-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .fw-plain-list li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #334155;
    padding: 0.3rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .fw-plain-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .fw-italic {
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .fw-limits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .fw-limits-label {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 0.375rem;
  }

  .fw-limits-label--may { color: #16a34a; }
  .fw-limits-label--maynot { color: #dc2626; }

  /* ── Axes diagram ────────────────────────────── */
  .fw-axes-diagram {
    background: #1e293b;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .fw-axes-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #94a3b8;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .fw-axes {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .fw-axis {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .fw-axis-line {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .fw-pole-end {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1e293b;
  }

  .fw-axis-arrow {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #4f46e5;
  }

  .fw-axis-desc {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #64748b;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── RAP flow ────────────────────────────────── */
  .fw-rap-flow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin: 1.75rem 0;
  }

  .fw-rap-phase {
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 560px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .fw-rap-phase--unlocked {
    border-color: #16a34a;
    background: #f0fdf4;
  }

  .fw-phase-num {
    position: absolute;
    top: -14px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    background: #4f46e5;
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .fw-phase-num--green {
    background: #16a34a;
  }

  .fw-rap-phase h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1e293b;
    margin: 0.25rem 0 0.375rem;
  }

  .fw-rap-phase p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: #475569;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .fw-phase-note {
    font-size: 0.875rem !important;
    color: #64748b !important;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 0.5rem !important;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .fw-rap-gate {
    background: #fffbeb;
    border: 1px solid #fde68a;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .fw-rap-gate h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #92400e;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .fw-rap-gate p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #78350f;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .fw-rap-gate ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.375rem;
  }

  .fw-rap-gate li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #78350f;
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.4rem 0.75rem;
    border-left: 3px solid #f59e0b;
  }

  .fw-rap-arrow {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  /* ── Pricing rule ────────────────────────────── */
  .fw-pricing-rule {
    background: #f8fafc;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-left: 3px solid #4f46e5;
    border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .fw-pricing-rule p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #334155;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* ── Nav ─────────────────────────────────────── */
  .fw-nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* ── Responsive ──────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .fw-poles-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .fw-limits-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .fw-nav {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .fw-method-row {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
